      "side": 1,
      "message": "In the design doc and in the frontend implementation, this defaults to [\u0027v.test_suite\u0027].\nIn the recipe module, this defaults to [] (by mistake).\n\nBut I\u0027m preferring defaulting to [] now.\nBecause in quite a few places (e.g. protobuf, validate.list), there is no clear distinction between [] and None/undefined.\nWe often needs another field to clearly communicate that the value is set to an empty array rather than left unspecified.\n\nIf we default to [\u0027v.test_suite\u0027], then we\n1. need an extra field to support [] (no extra column), or\n2. force every project to have at least one extra column.\nNeither is good.\n\nThis doesn\u0027t apply to grouping_keys, because forcing them to at least group by status is probably fine.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 40,
        "startChar": 17,
        "endLine": 40,
        "endChar": 31
      },
      "revId": "3706b0650fa5dd881a316c5443f690f868c50168",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba"
    },
